--- SOURCE 1: 宏观早报——2026年3月2日 ---
URL: https://www.sohu.com/a/991475638_121123900

SUMMARY:
<summary>
On March 1, 2026, China's National Committee of the Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference (CPPCC) announced that its 14th National Committee's fourth session will be held in Beijing on March 4, 2026. Separately, the Political Bureau of the CPC Central Committee held a meeting to discuss the draft outline for the 15th Five-Year Plan (2026-2030) and the government work report. According to Xinhua News Agency, the meeting emphasized continuing to implement a more proactive fiscal policy and a moderately loose monetary policy, strengthening the coordination between reform measures and macroeconomic policies. It also highlighted the need to build a strong domestic market, accelerate the cultivation of new growth drivers, and achieve high-level self-reliance in science and technology.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
中国人民政治协商会议第十四届全国委员会第四次会议于2026年3月4日在北京召开, 要继续实施更加积极的财政政策和适度宽松的货币政策,强化改革举措与宏观政策协同, 要着力建设强大国内市场,加紧培育壮大新动能,加快高水平科技自立自强
</key_excerpts>



