URL: https://q.stock.sohu.com/cn/600309/yjyg.shtml

SUMMARY:
<summary>
This webpage contains multiple performance forecasts for Wanhua Chemical (stock code 600309). The primary focus is the 2024 annual forecast, which indicates a year-over-year net profit decline of 22.49% to 1,303,306.66 thousand RMB, despite a 3.83% increase in revenue to 18,206,911.92 thousand RMB. Key reasons for the profit drop include stable gross margins amid price/cost fluctuations, increased R&D and operating expenses, and asset impairment provisions. The page also provides a historical view of performance forecasts from 2021 to 2023: 2023 saw a 3.57% net profit increase; 2022 saw a 34.12% decline due to rising input costs outpacing revenue growth; and 2021 saw a significant 145.47% surge in net profit driven by new capacity, strong demand, and favorable market conditions.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
预计2024年1-12月归属于上市公司股东的净利润为：1303306.66万元，与上年同期相比变动幅度：-22.49%。, 报告期内，公司实现营业收入18,206,911.92万元，较上年同期增长3.83%；归属于上市公司股东的净利润1,303,306.66万元，较上年同期下降22.49%。, 预计2023年1-12月归属于上市公司股东的净利润为：1681389.13万元，与上年同期相比变动幅度：3.57%。, 预计2022年1-12月归属于上市公司股东的净利润为：1623933.32万元，与上年同期相比变动幅度：-34.12%。, 预计2021年1-12月归属于上市公司股东的净利润为：2464874.81万元，与上年同期相比变动幅度：145.47%。
</key_excerpts>



