--- SOURCE 6: 胜宏科技入选2024年PCB企业营收百强排行榜 ---
URL: https://www.shpcb.com/newsshow-19-505-1.html

SUMMARY:
<summary>
On May 14, 2025, the "2024 China Electronic Circuit Industry Major Enterprise Revenue" list was jointly released by the China Electronics Information Industry Federation and the China Printed Circuit Association (CPCA). Shenghong Technology was recognized for its market performance and comprehensive strength, ranking 4th on the 2024 domestic PCB Top 100 list and 9th on the comprehensive PCB Top 100 list. According to CPCA statistics, 133 PCB enterprises were included in the revenue report (100 domestic, 33 foreign). In 2024, the combined revenue of the comprehensive PCB Top 100 was 3479.87 billion yuan, a year-on-year increase of 12.38%, while the combined revenue of the domestic PCB Top 100 was 1968.2 billion yuan, up 16.24%. The total revenue for all 133 enterprises was 3635.62 billion yuan, growing 12.25%. Four domestic companies achieved over 100 billion yuan in revenue: Dongshan Precision, Shennan Circuits, Jingwang Electronics, and Shenghong Technology.
