--- SOURCE 2: 十大券商最新策略！步入两会窗口，3月A股如何演绎？ ---
URL: http://m.toutiao.com/group/7612546209693155892/?upstream_biz=VolcEngine

SUMMARY:
<summary>
The webpage presents a summary of March 2026 market outlooks and investment recommendations from several major Chinese securities firms. Key themes include the potential for improved external risk conditions (e.g., US-China relations, US-Iran negotiations), expectations for further monetary and market liquidity easing, and continued economic and corporate profit recovery. Investment advice centers on policy-driven opportunities around the 'Two Sessions' (National People's Congress and Chinese People's Political Consultative Conference), with a focus on technology sectors (semiconductors, AI hardware, commercial aerospace), resources (metals, oil & gas), and public utilities. Firms highlight a shift from 'policy expectation' to 'earnings verification' later in the month, with 2025 annual reports and 2026 Q1 results becoming key anchors. Recommendations are structured around dual strategies of 'tech offense' and 'public utility defense' or focusing on resource and tech mainlines.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
中国银河：A股市场或将以政策催化为核心驱动力, 兴业证券：短期围绕涨价和政策两条线索，继续重视资源品与科技两大主线, 中泰证券：建议围绕“科技进攻、公用事业稳健”的思路进行组合配置, 3月建议继续逢低配置：一是政策和产业趋势向上的电子（半导体、AI硬件）、军工（商业航天）、通信（AI硬件）..., 3月中下旬，市场逻辑将从“政策预期”逐步转向“业绩兑现”
</key_excerpts>



