--- SOURCE 3: 最新消息!A股“变天”实锤，三大政策落地，下周行情定调! ---
URL: https://caifuhao.eastmoney.com/news/20260302085809338999480

SUMMARY:
<summary>
On March 2, 2026, an analysis piece highlights three major policy developments set to reshape China's A-share market, urging rational interpretation of claims of a market 'upheaval'. The three key policies are: 1) The new regulation on public offering funds, effective March 1, which mandates strict alignment between fund performance benchmarks and their strategies, aiming to stabilize 37 trillion yuan in assets and curb style drift. 2) The central bank's reduction of the foreign exchange risk reserve ratio for forward sales from 20% to 0% effective March 2, aimed at lowering corporate costs and encouraging foreign capital inflows. 3) The policy direction set by the upcoming '15th Five-Year Plan' for capital markets, emphasizing institutional inclusivity and support for future industries like quantum tech and AI. The market outlook predicts a structural rally led by themes like new quality productive forces and high-dividend blue chips, rather than a broad-based surge, and advises investors to focus on these core sectors while being wary of over-interpretation and volatility.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
严禁基金风格漂移，要求基金业绩基准必须与产品定位、投资策略高度匹配，一经确定不得随意变更。, 此举释放了监管层避免人民币过快升值的明确信号，有助于稳定外汇市场预期。, 政策明确支持量子科技、生物制造、氢能和核聚变能、脑机接口、具身智能、第六代移动通信等六大未来产业。, '变天'不等于全面上涨，而是市场风格更加清晰、主线更加明确。, 当前市场环境下，'选对赛道比努力更重要'。
</key_excerpts>



