URL: https://finance.sina.com.cn/stock/cpbd/2026-03-02/doc-inhppxwy5501365.shtml?cre=tianyi&mod=pcpager_news&loc=2&r=0&rfunc=9&tj=cxvertical_pc_pager_news&tr=174

SUMMARY:
<summary>
The State Council Tariff Commission of China has announced an adjustment to tariff measures on certain Canadian imports. Effective from March 1, 2026, to December 31, 2026, the previously announced 100% additional tariffs on Canadian oilseed meal and peas, and the 25% additional tariffs on Canadian lobster and crab, will not be imposed. This modifies the measures specified in the commission's 2025 Announcement No. 3.
</summary>

<key_excerpts>
自2026年3月1日至2026年12月31日,调整《国务院关税税则委员会关于对原产于加拿大的部分进口商品加征关税的公告》(税委会公告2025年第3号)规定的加征关税措施,不加征对原产于加拿大的油渣饼､豌豆加征的100%关税以及对原产于加拿大的龙虾､蟹加征的25%关税｡
</key_excerpts>



